<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>Grow Coding challenge</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles.css">
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: star-wars;
            src: url(shttps://allfont.es/allfont.css?fonts=star-jedi);
        }
        
        @font-face {
            font-family: intro-text;
            src: url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=News+Cycle:400,700);
        }
        
        .title {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            transform: perspective(300px) rotateX(25deg);
            height: 200px;
            width: 400px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 50px;
        }
        
        .text {
            color: #feda4a;
            font-family: 'star-wars';
        }
        
        .center {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .footer {
            font-family: "footer-text", sans-serif;
            color: #4bd5ee;
            font-weight: 100;
            letter-spacing: .1em;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            right: 0;
            text-align: right;
            color: #4bd5ee;
            font-family: 'intro-text';
            margin-right: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        html,
        body {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: black;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
    </style>

</head>


<body>
    <div class="center">
        <div>
            <h1 class="title text">WELCOME TO MY TEST</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="text">
            Please refer to one of the following endpoints:
            <ul>
                <li>/people <i>(remember you can sort them by adding /name, /height or /mass)</i></li>
                <li>/planets</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        Thanks! And may the force be with you . . .
    </div>
</body>

</html>